153
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:04,060
The fires of rebellion...
Do they continue to burn?!

154
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:06,100
All ships, to Onigashima!

155
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:07,440
Charge!

156
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:13,820
On the day Kaido killed
Oden twenty years ago...

157
00:11:13,820 --> 00:11:16,240
this country stopped moving forward!

158
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:19,370
No one deserves to be
laughed at when they die.

159
00:11:19,370 --> 00:11:22,660
What's wrong with a stranger
defending this land?!

160
00:11:22,660 --> 00:11:25,160
You say it! Aren't you an important person?!

161
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:28,540
You're the leader of these
great men, aren't you?!

162
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:32,710
I want to defeat Kaido!

163
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:41,720
Gum-Gum...

164
00:11:45,230 --> 00:11:46,600
Red...

165
00:11:47,940 --> 00:11:48,650
Roc!

166
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:14,670
Hey, Kaido! What are you doing?!

167
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:18,090
How the hell did he knock you down?!

168
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:23,760
I'm Monkey D. Luffy.

169
00:12:24,430 --> 00:12:26,680
The man who's gonna surpass you both...

170
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:32,610
and become the King of the Pirates!

171
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:03,730
Wealth, fame, power...

172
00:00:03,730 --> 00:00:07,990
Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
obtained everything the world has to offer.

173
00:00:07,990 --> 00:00:11,700
What he said in his final moments
drove countless souls to the seas.

174
00:00:11,700 --> 00:00:13,740
You want my treasure?

175
00:00:13,740 --> 00:00:15,580
Go ahead.

176
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:16,830
Find it!

177
00:00:16,830 --> 00:00:19,460
Everything is right where I left it!

178
00:00:21,750 --> 00:00:26,550
People set their sights on the Grand Line
in pursuit of their dreams.

179
00:00:26,550 --> 00:00:29,680
The world has truly entered
the Great Pirate Era!

